data.description: Lots of space in this lovely 4 bed, 3 bath home with full finished basement and second kitchen. There is even a second washer and dryer hookup in the basement which would make for a great extended family arrangement. Check out all the new finishes and updates in this new home to include 2 AC units, Smart thermometers, new ductwork, new paint, new LED lights, new fixtures in Kitchen and bath, slick ceilings, roof is only around 5 years new, and new insulated garage door. Home also features hardwood and tiled floors and stainless steel appliances. You, your family and guests will love the well designed floorplan and enjoy the many separate spaces this large home has to offer. The basement would work just perfectly for entertaining, movie night game room or large exercise room. You will love the covered back deck with TV connection that overlooks the mostly level back yard with raised garden bed. Community features great pool and clubhouse. Don't let miss out on this opportunity. An assumable loan option MAY be possible for you to get a much lower rate. Call the Powell Real Estate Team today to schedule your private tour.
